"```sql\nSELECT \n    (SUM(CASE WHEN superhero.eye_colour_id = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) - \n     SUM(CASE WHEN superhero.eye_colour_id = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS difference\nFROM \n    superhero\nWHERE \n    (superhero.weight_kg = 0 OR superhero.weight_kg IS NULL);\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the difference between the number of superheroes with blue eyes and those with no eye color among superheroes with missing weight data. It uses the conditions provided in the evidence to filter and compute the required values."